<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>You can find specific documents for this department using the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&publication_filter_option=all&topics%5B%5D=all&departments%5B%5D=companies-house&official_document_status=all&world_locations%5B%5D=all&from_date=&to_date=">publication search.</a>
 If the information you want is not published here, you can <a href="https://www.gov.uk/make-a-freedom-of-information-request">make a request for it</a>, under the Freedom of Information Act. 
You can also search through <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&publication_filter_option=foi-releases&topics%5B%5D=all&departments%5B%5D=companies-house&official_document_status=all&world_locations%5B%5D=all">previous responses to Freedom of Information requests</a>.</p>

<h2 id="who-we-are-and-what-we-do">Who we are and what we do</h2>

<p>This includes:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/companies-house">about us</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/companies-house#org-contacts">our contact details</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/companies-house/about/our-governance#organisational-chart">our structure</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/corporate-framework-document">our corporate framework</a></li>
</ul>

<h2 id="what-we-spend-and-how-we-spend-it">What we spend and how we spend it</h2>

<p>This includes:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?departments%5B%5D=companies-house&publication_type=corporate-reports">annual reports and reviews</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/companies-house/about/procurement">procurement</a></li>
</ul>

<h2 id="what-our-priorities-are-and-how-we-are-doing-and-progress">What our priorities are and how we are doing and progress</h2>

<p>Strategy, performance, plans and reviews.</p>

<p>This includes:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/companies-house-strategic-plan-2014-to-2019">our strategy</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/business-plan-2014-to-2015--2">our business plan</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&publication_filter_option=corporate-reports&topics%5B%5D=all&departments%5B%5D=companies-house&official_document_status=all&world_locations%5B%5D=all&from_date=&to_date=">annual report and accounts</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/companies-house-independent-adjudicators-report-2013-to-2014">independent adjudicators report</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/statistics?departments%5B%5D=companies-house">our statistics</a></li>
</ul>

<h2 id="how-we-make-decisions">How we make decisions</h2>

<p>Policy proposals, decision making processes, internal procedures,consultations.Our decision-making processes and records of our decisions can be found on <a rel="external" href="http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20140711134148/http://www.companieshouse.gov.uk/companiesAct/publications.shtml">the National Archive</a></p>

<p>These include:</p>

<ul>
  <li>consultation on late filing penalties (Companies Act 2006)</li>
  <li>government response to consultation on late filing penalties (Companies Act 2006)</li>
  <li>consultation on registrar’s rules (Companies Act 2006)</li>
  <li>government response to consultation on registrar’s rules(Companies Act 2006)</li>
  <li>consultations in relation to the Companies Acts</li>
  <li>minutes of meetings</li>
  <li><a rel="external" href="http://ico.org.uk/what_we_cover/audits_advisory_visits_and_self_assessments/audits">Information Commissioners Office audit</a></li>
  <li>examination procedures are available in hard copy by emailing the information rights team <a href="mailto:informationrights@companieshouse.gov.uk">informationrights@companieshouse.gov.uk</a>
</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="our-policies-and-procedures">Our policies and procedures</h2>

<p>Current written policies, procedures, guidelines for delivering our functions and responsibilities.This includes our: This includes our:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/companies-house/about/complaints-procedure">complaints procedure</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/companies-house/about/personal-information-charter">companies house personal information charter</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/companies-house-records-management-policy">records management policy</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/companies-house-information-security-and-assurance">information security and assurance</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/companies-house-accreditation-to-information-fair-traders-scheme">information fair trader scheme</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/companies-house-health-and-safety-policy-2014">health and safety policy</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/companies-house-environmental-policy"> environment policy</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/companies-house/about/equality-and-diversity">equality and diversity</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/companies-house/about/welsh-language-scheme">welsh language scheme</a></li>
</ul>

<h2 id="lists-and-registers">Lists and registers</h2>

<p>information held in registers required by law and other lists and registers relating to the functions of the authority</p>

<p>This includes:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a rel="external" href="http://wck2.companieshouse.gov.uk//dirsec">disqualified directors register</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?departments%5B%5D=companies-house&publication_type=foi-releases">freedom of information releases disclosure log information</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/standard-industrial-classification-of-economic-activities-sic">list of economic activities (sic)</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/companies-house/about/about-our-services#companies-house-fees">Companies House prices</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&publication_filter_option=forms&topics%5B%5D=all&departments%5B%5D=companies-house&official_document_status=all&world_locations%5B%5D=all&from_date=&to_date=">forms</a></li>
</ul>

<h2 id="the-services-we-offer">The services we offer</h2>

<ul>
  <li><a rel="external" href="http://wck2.companieshouse.gov.uk">Webcheck</a></li>
  <li>
<a rel="external" href="http://direct.companieshouse.gov.uk/">Companies House Direct</a> (CHD)</li>
  <li><a rel="external" href="https://ewf.companieshouse.gov.uk">Webfiling</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/companies-house-events-calendar/companies-house-events-calendar">events calendar</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/companies-house/about/access-and-opening">office access and opening times</a></li>
</ul>

<h2 id="open-data-and-datasets">Open data and datasets</h2>

<p>Datasets published by Companies House can be found on <a rel="external" href="http://data.gov.uk/">data.gov.uk</a></p>

<h2 id="requesting-information">Requesting information</h2>

<p>Alternatively you can write to us at:</p>

<div class="address"><div class="adr org fn"><p>

Information Rights
<br></br>Companies House
<br></br>Crown Way
<br></br>Cardiff CF14 3UZ 
<br></br>
</p></div></div>

<p>Please be specific about the information you want, as this will help us to find it for you.</p>

<h2 id="feedback-and-complaints-about-the-scheme">Feedback and complaints about the scheme</h2>

<p>We want our publication scheme to meet the needs of our customers and stakeholders. Any comments on or complaints about the scheme should be sent to the Information Rights Team at Companies House <a href="mailto:informationrights@companieshouse.gov.uk">informationrights@companieshouse.gov.uk</a></p>

